headline: Strength Seen in T. Rowe (TROW): Can Its 12.3% Jump Turn into More Strength?
summary: T. Rowe (TROW) witnessed a jump in share price last session on above-average trading volume. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions for the stock doesn't suggest further strength down the road.
